error.message: Parameter $entity_manager of method Drupal\cache_tools\CachewiseBlockViewBuilder::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityManagerInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0.
Call to deprecated method getPublishedEntityTypeCacheTag() of class Drupal\cache_tools\Service\CacheSanitizer.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to cache_tools.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
